research_summary:
Michael Fernandez is a partner in FGMK’s Audit and Accounting Practice and Quality Control Department. He has experience with SEC filings for large, multi-national public companies, as well as privately held corporations across multiple industries. He specializes in auditing and inspecting accounting estimates, including entity and intangible valuations. 

Fernandez's industry expertise include public and private company audits within airline, aerospace and defense; employee benefit plans; 
